### GET PRODUCT

GET {{url}}/api/product HTTP/1.1


### GET PRODUCT BY CATEGORY PARAMETER

GET {{url}}/api/product?category_id=1 HTTP/1.1


### POST PRODUCT

POST {{url}}/api/product HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category_id": 1,
  "name": "ラーメン",
  "price": 700
}


### POST MULTIPLE PRODUCT

POST {{url}}/api/products HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "category_id": 2,
    "name": "もやし炒め",
    "price": 750
  },
  {
    "category_id": 2,
    "name": "チャーハン",
    "price": 700
  },
  {
    "category_id": 2,
    "name": "パンケーキ",
    "price": 430
  },
  {
    "category_id": 2,
    "name": "カプチーノコーヒー",
    "price": 400
  }
]


### GET STATIC FILES

GET {{url}}/kitchen HTTP/2
